@node menus "Menus"

 Menus
 -----

 Project
    Open        Open a mode promotion file
    Save As     Save current settings to a file
    ----------
    Save        Make current ModePro settings permanent
    Last Saved  Load permanent settings
    ----------
    Enabled    Indicates whether or not ModePro is active
    ----------
    About...    Obvious
    ----------
    Hide        Hide interface
    Quit        Quit ModePro (all mode promotion stops)

 ScreenCatch
    Catch Programs
    Catch Screens
        If either of these option is enabled, when a program
        opens a screen, either the program's name or the screen's
        name or both will be added to the appropriate promotion
        list.  This is useful when you can't figure out the correct
        name to put in the list.
 
@endnode

